butions. With an increasing number of experimental groups\nemploying photoemission tomography to study adsorbate layers, we expect kMap.py\nto serve as an ideal analysis software to further extend the applicability of\nPT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2020 06:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 05:46:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 09:56:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-08"}
