ies of SNe Ia in two types of\nenvironments. Additionally, we find that blue SNe in low-mass environments are\nbetter standard candles than the others.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2020 11:55:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 25 Sep 2021 11:39:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
